{"tid":610442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新任公民教育委員會委員】孔泳淇稱DQ合理：新任議員應思量表達意見的方式","createTime":"2018-03-30T02:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T06:59:22.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eac04104f0a7c85adbe576e4b4efd15605636aee","tid":610442,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"政府公布新一屆公民教育委員會委員名單，其中有兩人經青年委員自薦試行計劃，獲委任為青年委員，當中包括港大社會科學學士（政治學與法學）5年級生、一國兩制青年論壇理事孔泳淇。孔向本報表示，目前政府在推廣《基本法》和公民教育意念等方法都是較單向，因此希望透過自己做義工和多年參加公民教育活動的經驗，在委員會內推動雙向性的推廣活動。<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孔泳淇又說，自己仍然是大學生，了解當下年輕人，「我覺得自己是貼地。」孔表示，修讀政治學是因為對政治有興趣，希望透過公共行政和政策研究等方法，去了解和改善社會。她坦言，未曾參加過六四晚會、七一遊行和佔中等活動，「我會睇新聞了解這些事件，但暫時不認為需要透過這些渠道，去表達意見。我傾向睇paper（論文）、研究其他國家地區如何用政策去處理社會問題。」孔續說，不太欣賞用佔領的抗爭方式，因為會影響民生，指當時的佔領運動對民生經濟有負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n孔泳淇說，讀書時正值政改爭議，因此修讀法學了解《基本法》。被問到覺得取消議員資格（DQ）是否合理，孔回應說：「合理的，因為立法會宣誓有其守則，（相關人士）不是無理被DQ，他們是在錯的時間、用錯了方式去表達意見。」孔認為，議員可以透過委員會和其他發言時間去表達意見，也希望新任的議員，可以思量自己表達意見的方式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180329/s00001/1522331362067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180329%2Fs00001%2F1522331362067&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bd9caac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180329%2Fs00001%2F1522331362067&h=38e3f397\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180329/s00001/1522331362067</a>"},{"pid":"651de991fccfa4d07db9ff8f84c68127ab2e62b4","tid":610442,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"睇新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB果d呀?"},{"pid":"0089e2182a335e954a330c8b2decf7f8ad684bde","tid":610442,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"651de991fccfa4d07db9ff8f84c68127ab2e62b4","tid":610442,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"睇新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB果d呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"KongU學生"},{"pid":"f66372f88ece634749cc48c1e2adad73edf2c74c","tid":610442,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"仆街我組媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6268fae95f3eee3ec26ad259539be17426134c","tid":610442,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:59:24.000Z","msg":"支持後生仔呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc955c2fcfff8630385f5fdb49af8ea53b16d15","tid":610442,"uid":6799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"成班投共鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e5714091af10c60bb723b46f94d61c96bdeb73","tid":610442,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66372f88ece634749cc48c1e2adad73edf2c74c","tid":610442,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"仆街我組媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"有無甜故？"},{"pid":"6613ae4917bcb29a08247ac11514d4546ce51da3","tid":610442,"uid":168171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"咁都叫合理？讀法律定係讀屎片？"},{"pid":"1d72374152e7fe8d3c26e2816c211e533ac280da","tid":610442,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f66372f88ece634749cc48c1e2adad73edf2c74c","tid":610442,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"仆街我組媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-